	Ledger video    
	 London, July 11 (PTI): A music video directed by Hollywood star Heath Ledger, his last work before his sudden death two years ago, is ready for official release.       
	The Brokeback Mountain star filmed the video for rapper NFAs single Cause An Effect shortly before he died from an accidental prescription drugs overdose in January 2008.    
	Helen role    
	 London (PTI): Academy Award-winning actress Helen Mirren will play nanny to comic Rusell Brand in the remake of Dudley Moores 1981 hit film Arthur. Her character is a reinterpretation of the original valet, the Daily Mail reported online.                                                                                                                                                      
